	<article id="post-183" class="post-183 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-blair category-democracy category-intelligence category-law category-politics category-spies category-talks-2 category-tours category-war-2 tag-accountability-2 tag-annie-machon tag-chris-coverdale tag-law-2 tag-make-wars-history tag-tony-blair tag-tour tag-war">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2009/05/my-entry.html" title="Permalink to Make Wars History UK Tour, 2009" rel="bookmark">Make Wars History <span class="caps">UK</span> Tour, 2009</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2009/05/my-entry.html" title="15:52" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2009-05-08T15:52:33+00:00" pubdate>May 8, 2009</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2009/05/my-entry.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>In Janu­ary and Feb­ru­ary 2009 Chris Cover­dale toured the <span class="caps">UK</span> speak­ing at Make Wars His­tory meet­ings.  I had the pleas­ure of intro­du­cing him at a num­ber of events.  The first date of the tour was in Liverpool:</p>
<p><object id="VideoPlayback" style="width: 500px; height: 410px;" value="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=2306392022896794653&amp;hl=nl" /><embed id="VideoPlayback" style="width: 500px; height: 410px;" width="320" height="240" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" src="http://video.google.com/googleplayer.swf?docId=2306392022896794653&amp;hl=nl" /></object></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
