egory tag">Shayler</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/war-2" title="View all posts in War" rel="category tag">War</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
